        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "At the same time, my dear, if they should condescend to reply to your communications-which our joint experience renders most improbable-far be it from me to be a barrier to your wishes.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
