        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "At times, even his impaired power of concentrating his memory and attention on particular points of business, has recovered itself very much; and he has been able to assist us in making some things clear, that we should have found very difficult indeed, if not hopeless, without him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
