        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "One, I paid for your articles, Trot, my dear; and the other two I have by me. When I lost the rest, I thought it wise to say nothing about that sum, but to keep it secretly for a rainy day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
