        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "'And indeed,' said Traddles, 'it was sold, by virtue of the power of management he held from you; but I needn't say by whom sold, or on whose actual signature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
