        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000073_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "He seemed to consider himself hardly less indebted to me, than to mr Micawber; which I consider (as I told him) quite a compliment.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000075_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000075_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "He is such an incarnate hypocrite, that whatever object he pursues, he must pursue crookedly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
