        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "Five hundred pounds?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000088_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000088_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "We both recommended a small sum in money, and the payment, without stipulation to mr Micawber, of the Uriah claims as they came in.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000088_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000088_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "To this, I added the suggestion, that I should give some explanation of his character and history to mr Peggotty, who I knew could be relied on; and that to mr Peggotty should be quietly entrusted the discretion of advancing another hundred.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000094_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000094_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "'There was-pardon me-really such a person, and at all in his power?' hinted Traddles.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000097_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000097_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "'You are quite right,' she said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000099_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000099_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "And don't any of you speak to me!' With that she smoothed her dress, and sat, with her upright carriage, looking at the door.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000101_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000101_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "We, being quite prepared for this event, which was of course a proceeding of Uriah Heep's, soon paid the money; and in five minutes more mr Micawber was seated at the table, filling up the stamps with an expression of perfect joy, which only that congenial employment, or the making of punch, could impart in full completeness to his shining face.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000101_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000101_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "To see him at work on the stamps, with the relish of an artist, touching them like pictures, looking at them sideways, taking weighty notes of dates and amounts in his pocket book, and contemplating them when finished, with a high sense of their precious value, was a sight indeed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1958_144503_000104_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1958/144503/1958_144503_000104_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1958",
        "content": "We passed the night at the old house, which, freed from the presence of the Heeps, seemed purged of a disease; and I lay in my old room, like a shipwrecked wanderer come home.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
